item.title: 1337CTF 2023
item.description: On the 17th-19th I participated in 1337 CTF, which was the time I participated as best I could with my team. With 1 difficult challenge, I stayed up until 4am looking for materials and missed the test. Both happy and sad. I’ll try harder anyway. Thank you to everyone on the team for supporting me.
